lts: lts (file time data)
lts:
lts: The lts set of utilities print file time data to standard output  
lts: similar to stat. They have been broken down due to portability
lts: considerations.
lts:
lts: The utilities are:
lts:
lts:   * lat - last access time
lts:   * lmt - last modification time
lts:   * lct - last change time
